# Next.js version 15 project

- the project uses pnpm for package management.
- The codebase uses drizzle-orm and postgres database.
- Please use [schema.ts](mdc:lib/db/schema.ts) and [queries.ts](mdc:lib/db/queries.ts) for data modeling and editing queries
- DO NOT implement queries directly in next.js action files, instead import them from [queries.ts](mdc:lib/db/queries.ts).
- DO NOT implement or call queries directely in client components, instead use action files.
